{"tid":845434,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人圈子入邊幾乎係0異性？","createTime":"2018-10-02T15:45:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T06:50:54.000Z","uid":208040,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"aae1326cb3ad68e0dd210ed1d408ef5443ba874a","tid":845434,"uid":208040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T15:45:20.000Z","msg":"中學即使係男女校 同班嘅永遠都係女多過男好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\njoin啲課外活動可以40個人先得一個男仔<br />\n校外programme又係同一個情況<br />\n入到U個系得兩個男仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上堂又冇乜同異性接觸嘅機會 分組project淨係會同返女仔一組 <br />\n想上支莊又係全女班咁濟<br />\n仲要以上識嘅男仔大部分都係矮毒柒是但中一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然咁冇咩唔好 但就係諗返起覺得幾奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家除咗中學個陣識落嘅男朋友同老豆 好耐冇同正常男仔講過野<br />\n唔通咁係迫我對男朋友專一<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9ae139884ec890d9b1e3215814ad268e6e02300","tid":845434,"uid":82450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T15:47:03.000Z","msg":"有"},{"pid":"0440a34cee33b82ca64afdd67bd8c4353dc7bc8f","tid":845434,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T15:49:00.000Z","msg":"同連登巴打講嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79eb69b0cdb2ddcb53017d61e6ba2443f50dfda2","tid":845434,"uid":69886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T15:50:09.000Z","msg":"你都係閪痕者 好想奶爆你個閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a625045a2664c1724c146149a75ae113c4a63e7","tid":845434,"uid":208040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0440a34cee33b82ca64afdd67bd8c4353dc7bc8f","tid":845434,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":